al minerals.<\/p>"}},"benefit_z84cbM":{"type":"benefit","settings":{"image":"","item_heading":"Camellia Oil","text":"<p>A lightweight, fast-absorbing oil rich in Omega 3 and 6 that nourishes the skin and enhances its natural glow.<\/p>"}},"benefit_yyayxB":{"type":"benefit","settings":{"image":"","item_heading":"Jasmine Sambac Oil","text":"<p>A luxurious, fragrant oil that boosts skin hydration and improves elasticity.<\/p>"}},"benefit_rqGJAE":{"type":"benefit","settings":{"image":"","item_heading":"Squalane","text":"<p>Olive-derived emollient that locks in moisture, protects the skin, and helps prevent signs of aging and hyperpigmentation.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["benefit_6AeHYd","benefit_z84cbM","benefit_yyayxB","benefit_rqGJAE"],"name":"t:sections.benefits_product.name","settings":{"advanced_heading":false,"heading":"","heading_richtext":"<h2>Your headline here<\/h2>","full-width-enabled":false,"section_height_mode":"fixed_height","desktop_section_height":79,"desktop_section_max_height":800,"desktop_width":72,"desktop_max_width":640,"button_label":"","button_link":"","quick_buy_product":"","button_select":"primary","size_heading":130,"size_heading_mobile":130,"color-overlay-opacity":100,"margin-top":0,"margin-bottom":92,"show_mobile_spacing":false,"margin-top-mobile":20,"margin-bottom-mobile":20}},"before_and_after_pwHcKh":{"type":"before-and-after","blocks":{"heading_pWNBpp":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Visible results* just after 7 weeks","disable_on_mobile":false,"size_heading":200,"size_heading_mobile":100}},"text_C3MDMr":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>*Based on a study of 120 users over 8 weeks<\/p><ul><li><em>99% noticeable skin improvement <\/em><\/li><li><em>80% reduction in acne<\/em><\/li><\/ul>","text_style":"body","disable_on_mobile":false}}},"block_order":["heading_pWNBpp","text_C3MDMr"],"name":"t:sections.before_and_after.name","settings":{"advanced_heading":false,"title":"","heading_richtext":"<h2>Before and after<\/h2>","layout":"image_first","before_image":"","after_image":"","desktop-percentage-image-width":50,"full-width-enabled":true,"slide_height":"adapt_to_content","desktop_fixed_height":320,"mobile_fixed_height":460,"enable_badges":true,"before_badge":"Before","after_badge":"After","section-color-overlay":"#f6f6f6","section-color-overlay-opacity":100,"color-overlay":"#eae5f9","color-overlay-opacity":100,"desktop_text_vertical_position":"center","desktop_text_horizontal_position":"left","mobile_text_horizontal_position":"left","margin-top":0,"margin-bottom":0,"show_mobile_spacing":false,"margin-top-mobile":20,"margin-bottom-mobile":20}},"rich_text_qMbkG4":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"icon_with_text_YXkmGa":{"type":"icon_with_text","settings":{"icon":"","select_icon":"bag","icon_alignment":"inherit","icon_alignment_mobile":"inherit","align_icon_top":false,"icon_advanced_settings":true,"icon_height_desktop":16,"icon_height":13,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0,"text":"<p>Rated 5 stars by our customers<\/p>","size_heading":100,"size_heading_mobile":100,"gap":8,"margin_top":8,"margin_bottom":8,"margin_left_desktop":0,"margin_left":0}},"heading_MBDxEx":{"type":"heading","settings":{"advanced_heading":true,"heading":"100% Natural Ingredients","heading_richtext":"<p>Loved by your skin. Trusted by many.<\/p>","disable_on_mobile":false,"size_heading":100,"size_heading_mobile":100,"heading_richtext_gradient":"linear-gradient(283deg, rgba(227, 205, 174, 1) 6%, rgba(221, 172, 106, 1) 78%)"}}},"block_order":["icon_with_text_YXkmGa","heading_MBDxEx"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"section_width":"regular","desktop_text_horizontal_position":"center","full-width-enabled":false,"background_gradient":"","margin-top":20,"margin-bottom":0,"show_mobile_spacing":false,"margin-top-mobile":20,"margin-bottom-mobile":20}},"testimonial_marquee_kUTKhC":{"type":"testimonial-marquee","blocks":{"image_DWFeYG":{"type":"image","settings":{"icon_select":"100","heading":"My skin has never looked this good","text":"<p><strong>I've tried countless serums and nothing came close.<\/strong> After using <strong>Beauty Glow Set <\/strong>for two weeks <strong>my skin is visibly plumper, the texture is smoother<\/strong> and my partner actually noticed the difference. This is my forever product.<\/p>","author":"<em>- Sophie M., verified customer<\/em>","icon_image_height_desk":50,"icon_image_height":40}},"image_yw99Yc":{"type":"image","settings":{"icon_select":"100","heading":"Finally a cream that doesn't break me out","text":"<p>As someone with reactive, sensitive skin I was so skeptical. But this cream in <strong>Beauty Glow Set<\/strong> is genuinely different - it absorbs instantly, doesn't clog my pores and my skin feels balanced all day. <\/p><p><strong>I repurchased three times already.<\/strong><\/p>","author":"- <em>Isabella K., verified customer<\/em>","icon_image_height_desk":50,"icon_image_height":40}},"image_YqdqMD":{"type":"image","settings":{"icon_select":"100","heading":"Obsessed doesn't even cover it","text":"<p>I use this face <strong>Beauty Glow Set <\/strong>and my skin is softer than it's ever been. The scent of cream is incredible and it doesn't leave that greasy film . <strong>My friends keep asking what I'm using.<\/strong><\/p>","author":"- <em>Zoe R., verified customer<\/em>","icon_image_height_desk":50,"icon_image_height":40}},"image_hkgXTJ":{"type":"image","settings":{"icon_select":"100","heading":"Dry skin? What dry skin?","text":"<p>I've struggled with dry patches on my face for years. This <strong>Beauty Glow Set<\/strong> sorted it within days - not weeks. My skin stays hydrated all day. Absolutely worth every penny.<\/p>","author":"- <em>Amelia T., verified customer<\/em>","icon_image_height_desk":50,"icon_image_height":40}},"image_dWT47h":{"type":"image","settings":{"icon_select":"100","heading":"The glow-up I didn't expect","text":"<p>I bought the serum and cream, cleanser, eye cream together as <strong>Beauty Glow Set <\/strong>and honestly I wasn't expecting much. Three weeks later my skin is glowing, my dark spots have faded and I've stopped wearing foundation to work.<\/p>","author":"- <em>Charlotte W., verified customer<\/em>","icon_image_height_desk":50,"icon_image_height":40}}},"block_order":["image_DWFeYG","image_yw99Yc","image_YqdqMD","image_hkgXTJ","image_dWT47h"],"name":"Testimonial: Marquee","settings":{"heading_richtext":"","text_style":"body","disable_auto_scroll":false,"animation_direction":"left","animation_speed":"150","card_width_desktop":475,"number_of_column_desktop":2.4,"gap_desk":24,"testimonial_text_size_desktop":100,"text_alignment_desktop":"left","card_width_mobile":280,"number_of_column_mobile":1.2,"gap":16,"testimonial_text_size":100,"text_alignment_mobile":"left","margin-top":0,"margin-bottom":36,"show_mobile_spacing":false,"margin-top-mobile":20,"margin-bottom-mobile":20}},"rich_text_Ag83CP":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_fazwEE":{"type":"heading","settings":{"advanced_heading":true,"heading":"100% Natural Ingredients","heading_richtext":"<p>Your 8-Week Glow Journey<\/p>","disable_on_mobile":false,"size_heading":100,"size_heading_mobile":100,"heading_richtext_gradient":"linear-gradient(283deg, rgba(227, 205, 174, 1) 6%, rgba(221, 172, 106, 1) 78%)"}},"text_Lyzeca":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Real results take time. Here's what to expect when you commit to the ritual.<\/p>","text_style":"body","disable_on_mobile":false}}},"block_order":["heading_fazwEE","text_Lyzeca"],"name":"t:sections.rich-text.presets.name","settings":{"section_width":"regular","desktop_text_horizontal_position":"center","full-width-enabled":false,"background_color":"#eae5f9","background_gradient":"","margin-top":32,"margin-bottom":8,"show_mobile_spacing":false,"margin-top-mobile":20,"margin-bottom-mobile":20}},"timeline_rhTYMU":{"type":"timeline","blocks":{"item_DVHcMF":{"type":"item","settings":{"time_heading":"After 1 week","time_heading_text_style":"headline","show_image":true,"image":"","heading":"The Fresh Start","heading_text_style":"headline","content":"<p>Your skin begins to feel the difference. After just seven days, you'll notice softer, more hydrated skin and a refreshed complexion. The Pink Cloud Cleanser balances your skin's pH, while Bakuchiol Serum and Aquarius Cream start working beneath the surface. Tightness, dullness, and that \"tired skin\" feeling fade away.<\/p><p><em>Expect: Smoother texture · Better hydration · A natural, healthy radiance<\/em><\/p>","reversed":false}},"item_3ifYfQ":{"type":"item","settings":{"time_heading":"Weeks 2–4","time_heading_text_style":"headline","show_image":true,"image":"","heading":"Visible Transformation","heading_text_style":"headline","content":"<p>Now the real magic shows. Pores look visibly clearer, breakouts calm down, and the under-eye area appears brighter as caffeine and marine algae reduce dark circles and puffiness. Your skin tone evens out, and the first signs of bakuchiol's smoothing effect on fine lines become noticeable.<\/p><p><em>Expect: Clearer pores · Reduced dark circles · More even skin tone · Fewer breakouts<\/em><\/p>","reversed":false}},"item_fkdgcM":{"type":"item","settings":{"time_heading":"Weeks 5–8","time_heading_text_style":"headline","show_image":true,"image":"","heading":"The Lasting Results","heading_text_style":"headline","content":"<p>This is where consistency pays off. Your skin reaches a new baseline - balanced, calm, and resilient. Redness and blemishes are minimized, fine lines and wrinkles appear visibly softened, and the under-eye area looks refreshed and youthful. Your complexion feels stable, healthy, and unmistakably glowing.<\/p><p><em>Expect: Stable, blemish-free skin · Reduced redness · Softened wrinkles · Brighter, lifted eye area · Long-lasting radiance<\/em><\/p>","reversed":false}}},"block_order":["item_DVHcMF","item_3ifYfQ","item_fkdgcM"],"name":"t:sections.timeline.presets.name","settings":{"heading_richtext":"","full-width-enabled":false,"text_style":"body","gap_desktop":48,"max_block_width":480,"time_heading_scale_desktop":120,"heading_scale_desktop":80,"gap_mobile":40,"time_heading_scale_mobile":100,"heading_scale_mobile":100,"color-progress-active":"#151515","color-progress-inactive":"#d4cdeb","color-overlay":"#eae5f9","color-overlay-opacity":100,"margin-top":20,"margin-bottom":20,"show_mobile_spacing":false,"margin-top-mobile":20,"margin-bottom-mobile":20}},"scrolling_icon_with_text_fVHm83":{"type":"scrolling-icon-with-text","blocks":{"icon_with_text_jtQL3z":{"type":"icon_with_text","settings":{"icon":"","select_icon":"heart","align_icon_top":false,"icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0,"text":"<p><strong>Radiant Glow<\/strong><\/p>","size_heading":100,"size_heading_mobile":100,"gap":6}},"icon_with_text_WtcK8i":{"type":"icon_with_text","settings":{"icon":"","select_icon":"none","align_icon_top":false,"icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0,"text":"<p><strong>Acne Reduction<\/strong><\/p>","size_heading":100,"size_heading_mobile":100,"gap":6}},"icon_with_text_fVGpd4":{"type":"icon_with_text","settings":{"icon":"","select_icon":"none","align_icon_top":false,"icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0,"text":"<p><strong>Reduced dark circles<\/strong><\/p>","size_heading":100,"size_heading_mobile":100,"gap":8}},"icon_with_text_qHBrEN":{"type":"icon_with_text","settings":{"icon":"","select_icon":"leaf","align_icon_top":false,"icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0,"text":"<p><strong>Antioxidant Defense<\/strong><\/p>","size_heading":100,"size_heading_mobile":100,"gap":6}}},"block_order":["icon_with_text_jtQL3z","icon_with_text_WtcK8i","icon_with_text_fVGpd4","icon_with_text_qHBrEN"],"name":"t:sections.scrolling_icon_with_text.name","settings":{"heading_richtext":"","full-width-enabled":true,"animation_speed":1,"spacing":72,"enable_dot_separator":false,"dot_size":"small","desktop_fixed_height":80,"mobile_fixed_height":60,"section-color-overlay":"#eae5f9","section-color-overlay-opacity":100,"color-body-text":"#151515","color-overlay-opacity":100,"margin-top":20,"margin-bottom":20,"show_mobile_spacing":false,"margin-top-mobile":20,"margin-bottom-mobile":20}},"collapsible_menu_with_image_dYLCTc":{"type":"collapsible-menu-with-image","blocks":{"collapsible_tab_rFJTXP":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"How long will this set last me?","content":"<p><strong>With twice-daily use, you can expect most products in this collection to last approximately 2-3 months. <\/strong><\/p><p>The cleanser may last longer since you're only using a small amount per wash, while the serum and eye cream will deplete faster due to daily morning and evening application. <\/p><p>Store products away from direct sunlight and heat to maintain their potency.<\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_xrUL8h":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"In what order should I use these products in my daily routine?","content":"<p>Your morning and evening routine should follow this sequence: <\/p><ol><li>Start by cleansing with <strong>Pink Cloud Rosewater + Tremella Cleanser<\/strong><\/li><li>Then apply <strong>Bakuchiol Serum<\/strong> to your face (avoiding the eye area), <\/li><li>Follow with a small amount of <strong>Corrective Eye Cream<\/strong> gently patted under the eyes, <\/li><li>Finish with <strong>Aquarius Pore Purifying Clarity Cream <\/strong>as your moisturizer. <\/li><\/ol><p>The rule is simple - always go from the lightest to the heaviest texture.<\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_NDfAd9":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Are these products suitable for my skin type?","content":"<p>This collection works for most skin types, but each product has its specialty. <\/p><p>Pink Cloud Cleanser is gentle enough for all skin types, including sensitive. <\/p><p>Aquarius Clarity Cream is specifically designed for oily and combination skin and is non-comedogenic. <\/p><p>Bakuchiol Serum is safe for sensitive skin and suitable for pregnant and breastfeeding women - unlike traditional retinol. <\/p><p>Corrective Eye Cream works for all skin types and is especially beneficial for those struggling with dark circles and puffiness.<\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_6R4hd9":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"How is bakuchiol different from retinol, and why should I choose it?","content":"<p><strong>Bakuchiol is a natural, plant-based alternative to retinol, sustainably sourced from the Ayurvedic Babchi plant.<\/strong> <\/p><p>It delivers similar benefits - smoothing fine lines and improving skin texture - <strong>without the common side effects of retinol such as irritation, redness, or sun sensitivity. <\/strong><\/p><p>You can safely use it both morning and night, and it's suitable during pregnancy and breastfeeding.<\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_DWyfex":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"How often should I use Corrective Eye Cream?","content":"<p>Apply the <strong>Green Tea Corrective Eye Cream <\/strong>twice daily - morning and evening. <\/p><p>Use a rice-grain sized amount for each eye and gently pat it along the orbital bone using your ring finger. <strong>You'll notice visible results - reduced dark circles and puffiness - after about 2-3 weeks of consistent use. <\/strong><\/p><p>The mineral mica in the formula provides an <strong>instant brightening effect around the eye area.<\/strong><\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}},"collapsible_tab_Q4r9WG":{"type":"collapsible_tab","settings":{"heading":"Will Pink Cloud Cleanser remove my makeup effectively?","content":"<p><strong>Pink Cloud is a gentle, creamy-jelly cleanser perfect for daily cleansing<\/strong> and removing light makeup. <\/p><p>For heavier or waterproof makeup, we recommend the double cleansing method - start with an oil-based cleanser or micellar water, then follow with Pink Cloud as your second cleanse. <\/p><p><strong>The pH-balanced formula cleanses without stripping or drying your skin.<\/strong><\/p>","open_by_default":false,"icon":"none","icon_advanced_settings":false,"icon_height_desktop":28,"icon_height":27,"icon_margin_desktop":0,"icon_margin":0}}},"block_order":["collapsible_tab_rFJTXP","collapsible_tab_xrUL8h","collapsible_tab_NDfAd9","collapsible_tab_6R4hd9","collapsible_tab_DWyfex","collapsible_tab_Q4r9WG"],"name":"t:sections.collapsible-menu-with-image.settings.presets.name","settings":{"heading_richtext":"<p>Got questions? We’ve got answers<\/p>","full-width-enabled":false,"layout":"image_first","desktop-percentage-image-width":42,"slide_height":"adapt_to_first_image","desktop_fixed_height":320,"mobile_fixed_height":460,"desktop_image":"","heading_font_style":"heading","menu_alignment":"center","section-color-overlay":"#f4f4fd","section-color-overlay-opacity":100,"color-collapsible-background":"#eae5f9","margin-top":60,"margin-bottom":60,"show_mobile_spacing":false,"margin-top-mobile":20,"margin-bottom-mobile":20}},"166064389763f114d4":{"type":"featured-collection","settings":{"advanced_heading":fal